{
  "texts": [
    "They also rated the level of negativity and positivity of the vignette on 5-point scales of \"not at all [negative/positive]\" (0) to \"extremely [negative/positive]\" (4).",
    "Reappraisal Quality.",
    "After reading the vignette-reappraisal pair, participants evaluated the quality of reappraisal on four dimensions by providing their level of agreement from 0 (strongly disagree) to 6 (strongly agree) to each of the following statements: Reappraisal Effectiveness -\"This rethinking is effective in reducing negative emotions or increasing positive emotions.\"",
    "Reappraisal Empathy -\"This rethinking is empathic.\"",
    "Reappraisal Novelty -\"This rethinking provides a novel interpretation to a situation that you have not thought about.\""
  ]
}